## 🏗️ Finance Fixes — PNL, Balance Sheet & Auto-Depreciation
- Zero food revenue (383,200 Ks real)
- Zero wallet consumed (50,700 Ks real)
- Only 800K salary as OPEX (10,012,666 Ks real)
