### 🎯 Sales Daily Lazy-Load Fix (07:02-07:08 UTC)

### Root Cause
- Dashboard is a Vue SPA with **lazy-loaded components**. The main JS was renamed to `.v2.js` (cache busting), but ALL lazy chunks still imported from `"./index-DDJXoolO.js"` (original path). Cloudflare had this path cached with OLD/WRONG content (n8n JS from when middleware was intercepting `/assets/*`).
- When clicking "Sales Daily":
- 1. Browser lazy-loads `SaleDaily-DXRSp17u.js` ✅
- 2. SaleDaily tries to import from `./index-DDJXoolO.js` ❌
- 3. Cloudflare serves CACHED n8n content for this URL
- 4. JavaScript fails → button does nothing

